      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">思齊.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>思齊大任，文王之母，思媚周姜。京室之婦，大姒嗣徽音，則百斯男。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Pure and reverent was Thâi Zăn,
The mother of king Wăn.
Loving was she to Kâu Kiang;—
​A wife becoming the House of Kâu.
Thâi Sze inherited her excellent fame,
And from her came a hundred sons.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
