      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">思齊.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>惠于宗公，神罔時怨，神罔時恫。刑于寡妻，至于兄弟，以御于家邦。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He conformed to the example of his ancestors,
And their spirits had no occasion for complaint.
Their spirits had no occasion for dissatisfaction;
And his example acted on his wife,
Extended to his brethren,
And was felt by all the clans and states.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
