      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">思齊.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>雝雝在宮，肅肅在廟。不顯亦臨，無射亦保。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Full of harmony was he in his palace;
Full of reverence in the ancestral temple.
Unseen (by men), he still felt that he was under inspection:
Unweariedly he maintained his virtue.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
