      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">思齊.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>肆戎疾不殄，烈假不瑕。不聞亦式，不諫亦入。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Though he could not prevent (some) great calamities,
His brightness and magnanimity were without stain.
Without previous instruction he did what was right;
Without admonition he went on (in the path of goodness).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-006__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
