      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·006.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">思齊.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>肆成人有德，小子有造。古之人無斁，譽髦斯士。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>So, grown up men became virtuous (through him),
And young men made (constant) attainments.
(Our) ancient prince never felt weariness,
And from him were the fame and eminence of his officers.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
